<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أخرجه أبو داود <span class="c2">(٢٧١٨)</span> وكذا الدارمى <span class="c2">(٢/٢٢٩)</span> وابن<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>